Package org.sakaiproject.genericdao.api.finders

These finder interfaces contain additional dependency safe functions which can extend the functionality of the GenericDao.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
AllFinder This Finder provides methods to find all persistent objects of a certain type
ByExampleFinder Deprecated. The example finder will be removed in the next version
ByPropsFinder Deprecated. Use BySearchFinder instead
BySearchFinder This finder includes methods to find persisted objects based on search restrictions, settings, limits, and order
Uses the Search object to control the search
 

Package org.sakaiproject.genericdao.api.finders Description

These finder interfaces contain additional dependency safe functions which can extend the functionality of the GenericDao.
These are explicitly for accessing persistent object data.
